# ============================================================================
# What to Commit
# ============================================================================
# ✓ Source code (*.py in core/, utils/, processing/, monitoring/, html_modules/)
# ✓ Entry points (reddarc.py, search_server.py, version.py)
# ✓ Templates (templates_jinja2/*)
# ✓ Static assets (static/css/*, committed static/js/*)
# ✓ SQL schema (sql/*)
# ✓ Docker configs (Dockerfile, docker-compose.yml, docker/*)
# ✓ Documentation (README.md, CONTRIBUTING.md, ARCHITECTURE.md, etc.)
# ✓ Configuration examples (.env.example)
# ✓ Tests (tests/*)
# ✓ GitHub templates (.github/*)
#
# ✗ Generated archives (output/, archive/, r/*, user/*)
# ✗ Input data files (*.zst, data/)
# ✗ Database files (postgres-data/)
# ✗ Logs and caches (*.log, .jinja_cache/)
# ✗ Python bytecode (__pycache__/)
# ✗ Virtual environments (.venv/)
# ✗ Secrets (.env)

# MCP Configuration (user-specific paths)
.mcp.json
